s Series Against Houston</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/18/baseball-west-virginia-evens-series-against-houston</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/18/baseball-west-virginia-evens-series-against-houston</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Armani Guzman" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/18/BSBvsHoustonApr18-55.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The No. 15 West Virginia University baseball team evened up its series with Houston on Saturday with a 7-1 victory at Kendrick Family Ballpark. The Mountaineers improve to 26-9 and 11-6 in the Big 12 while the Cougars fall to 17-20 and 4-13 in conference play.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/18/BSBvsHoustonApr18-55.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/18/BSBvsHoustonApr18-55.jpg"><media:title>Armani Guzman</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/18/BSBvsHoustonApr18-55.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 16:45:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59022</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Conclude Spring Work on Saturday</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/18/football-mountaineers-concluded-spring-work-on-saturday</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/18/football-mountaineers-concluded-spring-work-on-saturday</guid><category>Football</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="No alternative text provided." src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/18/858103948-sf_lh-4-18-lh-0016.jpg" /><br /><br />M